      • generateMaze

        void generateMaze(java.lang.String name,
                  int z,
                  int y,
                  int x,
                  algorithms.mazeGenerators.Maze3dGenerator mg)

        generateMaze

        Generate a 3d maze in a thread phool, according to arguments received. When finish, it throws a notification to the presenter to display it.

        Parameters:
        name - The maze name
        z - Total floors of maze
        y - Total rows of maze
        x - Total columns of maze
        mg - The generate algorithm class

      • solveMaze

        void solveMaze(algorithms.search.Searcher<algorithms.mazeGenerators.Position> searcher,
               java.lang.String name,
               java.lang.String type,
               algorithms.search.State<algorithms.mazeGenerators.Position> state)

        solveMaze

        Solve maze wanted according to the type ("hint" or "solve") and algorithm received. If state is not null, it change the initial position of the maze to it, so it calculte the solution from that position. When finish, it throws a notification to the presenter to display it.

        Parameters:
        searcher - The searcher algorithm class
        name - The maze name
        type - solution wanted. "hint" for half solution and back or "solve" for entaire solution
        state - a state from which the solution should be calculated

      • exit

        void exit()

        exit

        Shutdown all executors. i.e, executors won't accept new task. Also waits until all the task that have already been submitted finish what they are doing (or until the timeout is reached = which problably won't happen)

        displayCrossSection

      • loadData

        void loadData()
       throws java.lang.Exception

        loadData

        Load user data from SQL or zip file. If zip was required (in properties file) and there wasn't any last data, it create a new empty file.

        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - throws an exaption if the MySQL property value is invalid
